{"tid":570963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政協前委員雲大棉兒子車禍 搶救後延至下午3時43分不治","createTime":"2018-02-24T08:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T03:15:39.000Z","uid":41404,"like":298,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"0853b47aa826fdee3fba85bfa1b3d7bb4d59f231","tid":570963,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"一輛私家車清晨在上環失事，52歲司機受重傷，送院搶救延治下午3時43分不治。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者是全國政協前委員雲大棉的兒子雲維恩。<br />\n<br />\n至於涉事的私家車嚴重損毀，車頭撞至變形，前輪飛脫，零件散滿地，駕駛座位的安全氣袋彈出。<br />\n<br />\n事發清晨5時許，這輛私家車沿干諾道西天橋往西環方向行駛，駛至近西區海底隧道支路時失事，撞向路中的防撞欄，私家車衝前幾十米才停下。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382353-20180224.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382353-20180224.htm&d=ZSUkDF0cKWt9FWKYi9HxhhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=261b6b0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1382353-20180224.htm&h=7f04c0ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1382353-20180224.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f45a399d2b117f1110e801902bed0e71db0e84b4","tid":570963,"uid":116530,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd683b32d9dde9cb35a25dcb109834f2f88e372d","tid":570963,"uid":26752,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"會唔會被撞車<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/