" />"},{"pid":"9e78bb14a5c6bed708eedfccee59b46f33eaa238","tid":570963,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/162653_28ed0c2c598e1109941518190cd2bb87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F162653_28ed0c2c598e1109941518190cd2bb87.jpg&h=d7a7b013&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/24/162653_28ed0c2c598e1109941518190cd2bb87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F24%2F162653_28ed0c2c598e1109941518190cd2bb87.jpg&h=d7a7b013&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"737e2239882a0e4f4c9c9c1863aaa67702db7294","tid":570963,"uid":16193,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"原來咁多689爪牙係度，難怪雲大棉死左個仔人人讚好啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇清楚雲大棉乜嘢立場先，唔好下下見到「政協委員」就請小鳳姐⋯⋯"},{"pid":"deea6b1f178f2eaee6128b2c2d567e25dfdd112d","tid":570963,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc28d817908a7167b4bb426e026b804dabc299e9","tid":570963,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"737e2239882a0e4f4c9c9c1863aaa67702db7294","tid":570963,"uid":16193,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"原來咁多689爪牙係度，難怪雲大棉死左個仔人人讚好啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇清楚雲大棉乜嘢立場先，唔好下下見到「政協委員」就請小鳳姐⋯⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:49:15.000Z","msg":"佢係咩立場？"},{"pid":"d61b2c3a4c3ae4d3afdbd30fe59203e149c69417","tid":570963,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:52:39.000Z","msg":"齊鼓掌"},{"pid":"cc353947fe60dc4b2d940bb6e82d0640adb112d9","tid":570963,"uid":6604,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"港區政協名單公布，一向以敢言見稱的雲大棉被摒出局。左派圈子流傳，差三歲才到達七十歲必退界線的雲大棉，出局原因是他開罪了兩個人：中聯辦副主任鄒哲開和行政長官董建華。 <br />\n<br />\n兩個人都是為了一件事。據聞第二屆行政長官選舉時，鄒哲開不停約晤各選舉會議成員，為董建華拉票。在沒有競爭對手下，董當選是必然的事，但有關方面仍要做足措施，以防出現低票當選的不體面局面。<br />\n<br />\n鄒哲開推薦福建幫<br />\n但雲大棉卻一貫地不識抬舉，竟然問前來拉票的鄒哲開，有沒有中央文件叫他投董建華的票？有便拿出來，他才投票選董建華。鄒哲開當然沒有這樣一份中央文件。結果？雲大棉又得罪人。 <br />\n<br />\n想名字列入港區政協名單，第一關就要過鄒哲開。今次政協名單逾二十人是福建幫，正要多謝祖籍福建的鄒。雲大棉想過鄒哲開這關，不可能。 <br />\n確實，雲大棉言論「出位」，例如去年人大選舉他直言「有人造票」。<span style=\"color: red;\">就連《基本法》二十三條立法敏感問題，他也直指當局過於憂慮：「香港人連槍都冇，點（造）反呀？唔通支『香雞』反咩！</span>」他對董建華施政不留情面的諸多批評，更無日無之。氣量小的人，確實很難容忍他。 <br />\n但他「符合邏輯」地被摒出局，仍然叫人傷感。 <br />\n<br />\n我們的政府真不能容許一些憑良心講「唔聽」真話的人？但香港市民會感激他。"},{"pid":"268f9bad905caf04f981afb03d97d32173f5d926","tid":570963,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來咁多689爪牙係度，難怪雲大棉死左個仔人人讚好啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇清楚雲大棉乜嘢立場先，唔好下下見到「政協委員」就請小鳳姐⋯⋯</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政怯原來有好人！！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.