董建華。鄒哲開當然沒有這樣一份中央文件。結果？雲大棉又得罪人。 <br />\n<br />\n想名字列入港區政協名單，第一關就要過鄒哲開。今次政協名單逾二十人是福建幫，正要多謝祖籍福建的鄒。雲大棉想過鄒哲開這關，不可能。 <br />\n確實，雲大棉言論「出位」，例如去年人大選舉他直言「有人造票」。<span style=\"color: red;\">就連《基本法》二十三條立法敏感問題，他也直指當局過於憂慮：「香港人連槍都冇，點（造）反呀？唔通支『香雞』反咩！</span>」他對董建華施政不留情面的諸多批評，更無日無之。氣量小的人，確實很難容忍他。 <br />\n但他「符合邏輯」地被摒出局，仍然叫人傷感。 <br />\n<br />\n我們的政府真不能容許一些憑良心講「唔聽」真話的人？但香港市民會感激他。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d653228685a65a90385186e81eb6093ecc67730e","tid":570963,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374f5db8658ff4e76a6729576e28456dd49b0099","tid":570963,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:32:27.000Z","msg":"口德村村民全面進場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b657be8321f50de6b897e5257fee1f325c35332d","tid":570963,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813bc677b2645bd9a228292ab55274d4390c5d2f","tid":570963,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a315b76870596101d1186f00f07696a0aaa17fc","tid":570963,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64637f8dcde26466201b71644dd63dc34eaae5be","tid":570963,"uid":103156,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"737e2239882a0e4f4c9c9c1863aaa67702db7294","tid":570963,"uid":16193,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"原來咁多689爪牙係度，難怪雲大棉死左個仔人人讚好啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo